description:
Many downloadable ZIP archives have DIZ and NFO files included within them. Sure, they&amp;#039;re simple text files that can be viewed with Notepad, but GetDiz is a Windows freeware program especially designed for those files.

ASCII art is displayed correctly and the user interface is small, handy and specific.

Since the start of the GetDiz project more than 10 years ago the program has evolved into a full featured text editor. GetDiz can replace Notepad while maintaining an incredible speed, ease of use and small size. Version 4 includes Windows Vista support and many new options including auto-copy, one instance mode and automatic window resize according to file dimensions.

